title: NFL Around the League: Week 1 Recap - September 8th, 2013
itunes:title: NFL Around the League: Week 1 Recap - September 8th, 2013
description:
A room full of heroes, Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling break down everything you need to know about all of the Week 1 action. Get caught up on all the analysis and key takeaways from each game. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.
